snippet.title: Spectrolite - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Spectrolite is available on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1694880/Spectrolite/
Join the community on Discord: https://discord.gg/hegHtGRmt6


Spectrolite is a challenging first-person platformer set in futuristic environments. Combine parkouring with powerful abilities, test your skills in fast paced timed challenges, and follow the call of a mysterious specter while travelling through a ruined world.

-------------------------------
